texts.text: Over there!
*Howl*
*Yell*
Hmph!
*Groan*
We're in the belly of the beast. Their defense is airtight.
Still, we've managed to open a path.
Thanks to Nergal, that is.
I couldn't have done this alone.
However, we can't relax just yet. Tiamat is a mighty foe.
No surprise there. The air feels heavier the closer we get.
This ain't gonna be easy.
...! I think I see her.
>They take down multiple demons, and soon enough...
>Tiamat's hulking frame comes into view.
So, you're the humans who have been slaughtering my servants.
It's Tiamat. From this proximity, you can sense her true size.
And she's got "I'll crush you" written all over her face.
Hey, Boss Lady. We know you've been runnin' wild in our world.
That ain't gonna fly for us though, so just go home already.
Do not toy with me. I know Marduk is in this world.
I will not return until I have found and killed him!
Talk about pushy. We're the ones gettin' sucked into your drama.
You can't reason with her. She's a monster bound by vengeance.
...! You are...!
I...I know this aura...! It is just like his!
Do you recognize me, Tiamat?
I am Nergal, son of the wind god Enlil.
It was my father who commanded Marduk to slay you.
Marduk... Enlil...
Arghhhhhhhhh!!
>With a mighty roar, Tiamat releases a burst of power.
Wh-Whoa! What's with this energy?!
The air and ground are shaking...
Our bodies too... It's crazy.
I can see why you recruited us, Nergal.
A single moment of hesitation will lead to certain death.
I trust you're ready, Liberators?
Absolutely.
Just a minute.
Haha! That's our Newbie.
We must stay strong, Newbie. There's no room for error.
Let's go, y'all!
Devil Download!!
>The summoned demon allies strike Tiamat together.
Shiang! We'll attack from the left!
Understood! Then we'll take her from the right!
Ririn, please join me!
Okay! Let's show her our Lovey-Dovey Attack!
>The Liberators attack as they taunt Tiamat.
>However...
Such measly power cannot harm me!
You've gotta be kidding me.
Our attacks are useless...?
Damn! I figured she was tough, but this is...
Do not falter. We'll attack as one!
Gotcha! Let's goooooo!
*Yell*
>Nergal and Megakin attack at the same time.
>Unfortunately, they still fail to lay a scratch on Tiamat.
Man, what's with this chick...?
Is that all?
Do not think for one moment that you can beat my raaaaage!!
...! Everyone, get down!
>Tiamat's howl emits a huge shock wave.
>It swiftly wipes out the Liberators' demon allies.
Ngh... I can't believe it...
She took out our demons in one hit...
Shoot, at this rate...
Megakin! Fall back! If we're too stubborn, people will die!
Tch! Guess we've got no choice...
Everyone, retreat! Let's get outta here, ASAP!
Hmph! ...Understood.
>They obey Megakin and escape from the battlefield.
Nergal! Humans! I will find you!
I will offer your heads to my late husband Apsu!
We got away somehow.
Great. At least it wasn't a total shitshow.
Don't talk like that. She was stronger than anyone expected.
Our apologies, Nergal. We failed you.
I, too, misjudged her power.
Now that it's come to this, I must play the ace up my sleeve.
You have another plan?
It's a secret finishing move.
I'll briefly return to my own world to obtain it.
Our next fight will be her last. Rest while you can.
He's gone.
A secret Tiamat Crusher, huh? Well, it's our best bet for now.
Let's take a breather. We'll be brawlin' again in no time.
...! Looks like someone's got other plans.
There you are. You're the mortal nuisances who stand in our way.
I shall take those heads for Tiamat.
Tch. Read the room, ya world-hoppin' hobgoblin!
